sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Envoy as Envoy Proxy<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (ext-proc)<br/>6789/TCP gRPC
    participant MS as Model Server Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,MS: Flow 1: Inference Request (Optimized Baseline)
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80 (no auth by default)
        GW->>Envoy: Forward request<br/>HTTP/80
        Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc consultation<br/>gRPC/6789 (no TLS)
        EPP->>MS: Poll /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000 (KV-cache, queue depth)
        MS-->>EPP: Prometheus metrics
        EPP-->>Envoy: Routing decision<br/>(selected pod endpoint)
        Envoy->>MS: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000 (no TLS)
        MS-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/SSE 8000/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,MS: Flow 2: Prefill/Decode Disaggregation
        participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
        participant Decode as Decode vLLM<br/>8200/TCP HTTP
        participant Prefill as Prefill Pod<br/>8000/TCP + 5600/TCP

        Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
        GW->>Sidecar: Route to decode pod<br/>HTTP/8000
        Sidecar->>Decode: Forward internally<br/>HTTP/8200
        Decode->>Prefill: KV-cache transfer request<br/>NIXL/5600 (no encryption)
        Prefill-->>Decode: KV-cache data<br/>NIXL/5600 (no encryption)
        Decode-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTP/SSE 8000/TCP
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Prom,OTEL: Flow 3: Observability
        Prom->>MS: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8000 (30s interval)
        Prom->>EPP: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/9090 (30s interval)
        MS->>OTEL: Export traces<br/>gRPC OTLP/4317 (no TLS)
        EPP->>OTEL: Export traces<br/>gRPC OTLP/4317 (no TLS)
    end
